17
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:18,590
- Hurry and come here.
- I'm calling for you.

18
00:02:19,150 --> 00:02:20,119
Me?

19
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:22,750
Hello. Congratulations.

20
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:25,359
You'll make a short film
for our wedding, right?

21
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,839
That's right. You can call me Zhou.

22
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,869
We don't have high expectations.

23
00:02:28,870 --> 00:02:30,399
We just want

24
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:33,430
