a Korean drama vibe.

27
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:41,920
What do you mean by that?
Do you not know how to do it?

28
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:44,280
I do have no idea how to create
a Korean drama vibe for you.

29
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:46,029
