31
00:02:47,270 --> 00:02:48,309
We want a Korean drama vibe!

32
00:02:48,310 --> 00:02:49,519
Follow my wife's instructions!

33
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,269
He can. Let me introduce him.

34
00:02:51,270 --> 00:02:53,149
This is the movie director

35
00:02:53,150 --> 00:02:54,799
that we've hired with plenty of money.

36
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:55,749
He has won awards before.

37
00:02:55,750 --> 00:02:56,429
Is that so?

38
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:58,309
You guys want
a Korean drama vibe, right?

39
00:02:58,310 --> 00:03:00,310
That's his expertise. Am I right?

40
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:01,029
Do it.

41
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:01,359
Yeah.

42
00:03:01,360 --> 00:03:02,309
Hurry and do it!

43
00:03:02,310 --> 00:03:03,899
- Here. Calm down.
- Can you do it or not?

44
00:03:03,899 --> 00:03:04,639
Yes, I can.

45
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:06,239
- Come on.
- Okay. Let me tell you this.

46
00:03:06,239 --> 00:03:08,589
I want a Korean drama vibe.

47
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:09,839
The kind with pink bubbles.

48
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,149
Pink bubbles. Do you understand?

49
00:03:11,150 --> 00:03:12,429
You mean Teletubbies?

50
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:14,239
- Hey! What was that?
- I'll handle this.

51
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:16,239
- What kind of attitude was that?
- What do you mean?

52
00:03:16,239 --> 00:03:18,309
We paid you! We hired you
with a lot of money!

53
00:03:18,310 --> 00:03:19,429
Scram if you can't do it!

54
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,269
Please wait.

55
00:03:20,270 --> 00:03:21,590
