to photoshop the bubbles?

63
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:33,840
Yeah. Do it.

64
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:34,929
Yeah, we're done discussing.

65
00:03:34,929 --> 00:03:36,520
- No problem.
- His Mandarin is terrible.

66
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:38,780
- He's a director from the U.S. Come.
- Let's do it, then.

67
00:03:39,150 --> 00:03:40,149
Remember this.

68
00:03:40,150 --> 00:03:42,869
Make me look like Song Hyekyo later.

69
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:46,119
Make my husband
look like Hyun Bin, got it?

70
00:03:46,120 --> 00:03:47,380
Alright, Mr. Hyun.

71
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,060
My surname is Xie!

72
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,469
Are you an idiot?

73
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:52,399
What's going on up there?

74
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,749
Are you an idiot?

75
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:56,100
Dai Daji, stop hiding. Show yourself.

76
00:03:57,270 --> 00:03:58,500
Director Wen.

77
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,820
Please go ahead.

78
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:02,780
Don't you guys know
what we're doing today?

79
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,919
Today we're shooting beauty models.

80
00:04:04,920 --> 00:04:07,060
What's the product ad for today?

81
00:04:07,640 --> 00:04:08,869
Hailan Beauty

82
00:04:08,870 --> 00:04:10,839
Royal Seaweed Golden Hydrating Mask.

83
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:13,079
Don't you guys think something's off?

84
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:13,990
Yeah. Something's off.

85
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:17,709
Who will put on facial masks

86
00:04:17,710 --> 00:04:19,709
with a revealing outfit
with thick makeup on?

87
00:04:19,710 --> 00:04:20,990
What else are we supposed to do?

88
00:04:21,230 --> 00:04:22,839
They want models with no makeup on.

89
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,469
No makeup!

90
00:04:23,470 --> 00:04:25,870
Tell them to remove their makeup.
If not, you guys are fired!

91
00:04:28,910 --> 00:04:31,230
We won't remove our makeup.

92
00:04:33,710 --> 00:04:34,959
- Miss.
- Please have some water.

93
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,029
Please.

94
00:04:36,030 --> 00:04:38,009
You guys didn't say
that we had to remove our makeup.

95
00:04:38,009 --> 00:04:39,829
Put some sketchy,
unverified product on my face?

96
00:04:39,829 --> 00:04:42,290
Can you afford to compensate us
if anything happens to our faces?

97
00:04:42,290 --> 00:04:44,320
I spent 50 yuan
to get my makeup done in a hair salon.

98
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:45,439
Now, you want me to remove it?

99
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:48,149
- Sisters, can you just do us a favor?
- Who are you calling sisters?

100
00:04:48,150 --> 00:04:50,029
Girls, there's another job coming in.

101
00:04:50,030 --> 00:04:50,909
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

102
00:04:50,910 --> 00:04:52,469
Wait. You can't just leave like this.

103
00:04:52,470 --> 00:04:54,269
I'll give you guys an extra 50 yuan.

104
00:04:54,270 --> 00:04:56,550
- Forget about it.
- 100 yuan? 150 yuan?

105
00:04:56,710 --> 00:04:58,020
500 yuan, and it's a deal.

106
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:02,430
We don't have that much.

107
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,399
Is this okay?

108
00:05:04,400 --> 00:05:05,149
Higher.

109
00:05:05,150 --> 00:05:06,319
Higher?

110
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:07,109
Higher.

111
00:05:07,110 --> 00:05:07,999
Higher?

112
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,399
- That's right.
- What about this?

113
00:05:09,400 --> 00:05:10,789
- That looks nice.
- Okay?

114
00:05:10,790 --> 00:05:13,670
- Can you go any higher?
- I'm at my limits.

115
00:05:13,790 --> 00:05:15,319
Remember this.

116
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:17,229
This is my most beautiful angle.

117
00:05:17,230 --> 00:05:17,959
Alright.

118
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,269
You need to highlight

119
00:05:19,270 --> 00:05:20,519
my husband's long legs.

120
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:23,669
Make him look like
a Korean oppa who's 185 cm tall.

121
00:05:23,670 --> 00:05:25,790
So, you need to lower the angle.

122
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:27,519
- Come. Give it a try.
- Let's try it.

123
00:05:27,520 --> 00:05:28,880
- An elevated shot.
- Give it a try.

124
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,319
Come on. Highlight my long legs.

125
00:05:30,320 --> 00:05:31,870
Long legs, huh?

126
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:32,839
Is this okay?

127
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,469
- You two are a perfect match.
- Lower.

128
00:05:34,470 --> 00:05:35,999
Lower!

129
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,319
Crawl on the floor!

130
00:05:37,320 --> 00:05:38,620
- Crawl down!
- Be careful.

131
00:05:38,710 --> 00:05:40,349
Highlight my long legs!

132
00:05:40,350 --> 00:05:41,670
Alright.

133
00:05:43,150 --> 00:05:44,079
You look so cool.

134
00:05:44,080 --> 00:05:45,750
Alright.

135
00:05:46,110 --> 00:05:47,319
I have a question.

136
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:49,399
What should I do when you two
are in the same frame?

137
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:50,519
When we're in the same frame,

138
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,669
just film me from a high angle

139
00:05:51,670 --> 00:05:53,319
and film him from a low angle.

140
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:54,959
If so, you two won't match on screen.

141
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,230
What should I do, then?

142
00:05:56,560 --> 00:05:58,589
Just photoshop it.
Do you know how to use MeituPic?

143
00:05:58,590 --> 00:06:00,959
- Yeah. Aren't you a director?
- OK. He can do that.

144
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:03,380
- How can I photoshop this?
- Leave if you can't do it!

145
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:05,229
They haven't paid us yet.

146
00:06:05,230 --> 00:06:07,199
You better do it
if you want to make money.

147
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:09,319
I quit! I want to go home!

148
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:13,709
Yeah, I can do it.

149
00:06:13,710 --> 00:06:16,079
- Stop being angry.
- Congratulations on your wedding.

150
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:19,029
What do you mean by they're gone?
The brand dealers will arrive soon.

151
00:06:19,030 --> 00:06:20,349
What do you expect them to do?

152
00:06:20,350 --> 00:06:22,199
Do you want them
to stare at each other on stage?

153
00:06:22,200 --> 00:06:23,269
Now, we can't do anything.

154
00:06:23,270 --> 00:06:26,080
Do you want the production team
to pay the price for your stupidity?

155
00:06:29,000 --> 00:06:30,269
Director Wen, give me a second.

156
00:06:30,270 --> 00:06:32,060
I have a backup plan.

157
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:33,550
Jingshu.

158
00:06:33,790 --> 00:06:34,700
Jingshu?

159
00:06:36,030 --> 00:06:37,430
Don't be nervous.

160
00:06:37,710 --> 00:06:39,060
Director Wen, take a look.

161
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,940
What do you think about her?

162
00:06:41,440 --> 00:06:43,559
Hello. My name is Shen Jingshu.

163
00:06:43,560 --> 00:06:45,029
Come again?

164
00:06:45,030 --> 00:06:46,430
Shen Jingshu.

165
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:48,550
My name comes from a line
in the Book of Songs.

166
00:06:48,670 --> 00:06:49,999
"The reticent girl is truly lovely.

167
00:06:50,000 --> 00:06:51,620
She waits for me at a city corner.

168
00:06:51,670 --> 00:06:54,670
She hides so that I can't see her,
and I get puzzled and antsy."

169
00:06:55,910 --> 00:06:57,149
Alright. We'll use her.

170
00:06:57,150 --> 00:06:58,380
Get ready.

171
00:06:58,740 --> 00:07:00,999
Jingshu, it's fine.
There's nothing you need to worry about.

172
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:03,430
Just remember to hold this logo
in the correct position.

173
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,199
- Like this?
- Good. Don't be nervous.

174
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,589
Now, Beautiful.

175
00:07:06,590 --> 00:07:07,029
Next,

176
00:07:07,030 --> 00:07:07,879
let us welcome

177
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:12,260
our special guest for the night.

178
00:07:14,760 --> 00:07:16,439
A new revolution in skin whitening,

179
00:07:16,440 --> 00:07:18,460
a new approach to hydration.

180
00:07:18,590 --> 00:07:21,910
In seven days,
it'll turn you into Snow White.

181
00:07:22,230 --> 00:07:23,909
Dry and dull skin?

182
00:07:23,910 --> 00:07:25,029
There's no need to fear.

183
00:07:25,030 --> 00:07:26,839
Oily skin during hot weathers?

184
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:27,990
There's no need to fear.

185
00:07:28,030 --> 00:07:30,439
Hailan Beauty Royal Seaweed
Golden Hydrating Mask

186
00:07:30,440 --> 00:07:33,060
knows you the best.

187
00:07:34,520 --> 00:07:36,700
Thank you for introducing
such a great product.

188
00:07:36,910 --> 00:07:38,319
Not bad at all.

189
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,620
She did great.

190
00:07:42,270 --> 00:07:44,020
Daji!

191
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:49,669
- Hold this for me.
- One, two, three.

192
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:51,659
- What's wrong?
- Can't you even do some basic Math?

193
00:07:51,659 --> 00:07:53,269
Hurry. We're in trouble.

194
00:07:53,270 --> 00:07:55,160
