- What if we can't resolve the issue?

195
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,670
- What's going on?
- You!

196
00:07:57,350 --> 00:07:59,350
You're in charge of
the product placement, right?

197
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:00,430
I...

198
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:02,199
What's wrong?

199
00:08:02,200 --> 00:08:04,709
We brought four
new necklaces here today.

200
00:08:04,710 --> 00:08:06,519
Why are there only three left?

201
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,870
There's also a platinum one.

202
00:08:08,030 --> 00:08:10,230
That can't be.
We placed everything on the table.

203
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,910
Why would one be missing?

204
00:08:13,110 --> 00:08:14,359
I think... I'm sure it's still here.

205
00:08:14,359 --> 00:08:16,900
We placed everything on the dressing table.
Didn't you search it thoroughly?

206
00:08:16,900 --> 00:08:18,789
