207
00:08:18,790 --> 00:08:19,589
It's not here?

208
00:08:19,590 --> 00:08:21,060
You have to take responsibility.

209
00:08:22,590 --> 00:08:23,639
How?

210
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,820
You have to compensate us.

211
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:26,519
Me?

212
00:08:26,520 --> 00:08:28,079
This necklace costs over 10,000 yuan.

213
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:29,380
I can't afford to compensate you.

214
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:31,190
I don't care.

215
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:36,039
Miss, I'm just an intern.

216
00:08:36,040 --> 00:08:38,510
I only make 200 yuan per episode we do.

217
00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:41,340
I can't afford
to compensate you for this.

218
00:08:41,470 --> 00:08:43,839
- And, it's not my fault...
- Fine.

219
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,910
Forget it.

220
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:47,060
I'll talk to Director Wen.

221
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:48,629
- Director Wen!
- Wait!

222
00:08:48,630 --> 00:08:51,199
Please don't!
Please don't look for Director Wen.

223
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,109
What about this?
I'll think of something.

224
00:08:53,110 --> 00:08:54,820
You better come up with a solution.

225
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,060
Don't fall behind.

226
00:08:58,110 --> 00:09:00,030
Please don't tell Director Wen.
Thank you.

227
00:09:02,230 --> 00:09:03,630
What's going on?

228
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,940
Daji,

229
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,079
calm down.

230
00:09:07,080 --> 00:09:08,709
You can have my pay this time.

231
00:09:08,710 --> 00:09:09,439
No way.

232
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,959
I'll get angry if you keep doing this.

233
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,310
Hurry and keep it away.

234
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:14,060
What's yours is yours.

235
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,340
I'll come up with a solution.

236
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:19,989
Like what? Let's head back
and discuss this with Zhou Shui.

237
00:09:19,990 --> 00:09:20,989
No.

238
00:09:20,990 --> 00:09:22,510
You mustn't tell him.

239
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:25,060
He's busy with a movie shooting lately.

240
00:09:25,920 --> 00:09:29,159
Ladies and gentlemen, the bride
and her father will enter the hall now.

241
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:31,390
Please give them a big hand.

242
00:09:33,990 --> 00:09:35,199
