251
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:07,060
Look into her eyes.

252
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,150
Here you go.

253
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:27,919
Mister, how much do they cost?

254
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:30,199
It contains two meat and one vegetable.
15 yuan each.

255
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,340
It's that expensive?

256
00:10:32,470 --> 00:10:33,910
How much do the buns cost?

257
00:10:33,990 --> 00:10:36,469
The buns?
I'll charge you one yuan per bun.

258
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:37,959
Alright. I'll take two.

259
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:38,319
Okay.

260
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,550
Two buns, coming up.

261
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,559
The soup is free, right?

262
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:42,589
That's right.

263
00:10:42,590 --> 00:10:43,860
You can serve yourself over there.

264
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:49,559
Dai Daji? I thought it was you
when I saw you from afar.

265
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:50,989
I never expected it to be you.

266
00:10:50,990 --> 00:10:52,550
Aren't you Yiming?

267
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:54,039
Long time no see.

268
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:57,389
- We last met when...
- When I was trying to get into Beijing.

269
00:10:57,390 --> 00:10:58,199
That's right.

270
00:10:58,200 --> 00:11:01,120
My mom organized a meal with her colleagues.
Your mom brought you there.

271
00:11:01,470 --> 00:11:02,980
- Let me serve you.
- What a coincidence.

272
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:05,919
Back then,
Mom told me to learn from you.

273
00:11:05,920 --> 00:11:08,159
The wall of photos
right after our university's entrance

274
00:11:08,160 --> 00:11:09,920
still has a photo of you
holding a guitar.

275
00:11:09,920 --> 00:11:11,550
Don't bring that up.
It's so embarrassing.

276
00:11:11,870 --> 00:11:12,989
What are you doing here?

277
00:11:12,990 --> 00:11:14,229
I'm working here.

278
00:11:14,230 --> 00:11:16,749
What's with your meal?

279
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:18,190
How could that fill your tummy?

280
00:11:19,080 --> 00:11:20,679
I'm on a diet lately.

281
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:22,109
You know?

282
00:11:22,110 --> 00:11:23,079
Alright. Thank you.

283
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,910
I should eat lighter food.

284
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:26,670
Yiming, what are you doing here, then?

285
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:29,559
The viewer rating of your show
has plummeted.

286
00:11:29,560 --> 00:11:31,469
Your superior called me here
to discuss how

287
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:33,270
we should report it to our superiors.

288
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,790
Are you from the HQ?

289
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:35,940
I'm affiliated.

290
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:38,030
It's all for the sake
of my Beijing hukou.

291
00:11:38,920 --> 00:11:40,839
So, you have a Beijing hukou now?

292
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:42,319
My goodness, Yiming.

293
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:45,190
I suppose you're a Beijinger now.

294
00:11:45,350 --> 00:11:46,349
I guess so.

295
00:11:46,350 --> 00:11:48,079
After all, I just bought a house here.

296
00:11:48,080 --> 00:11:49,470
You already bought a house here?

297
00:11:49,470 --> 00:11:51,480
I bought it by installments.
It isn't that expensive.

298
00:11:51,750 --> 00:11:53,679
I'll invite you
once I'm done with the renovation.

299
00:11:53,680 --> 00:11:55,910
Sure. You're so successful.

300
00:11:56,080 --> 00:11:57,389
What about you? How are you doing?

301
00:11:57,390 --> 00:11:59,279
What kind of position do you have?

302
00:11:59,280 --> 00:12:01,559
I follow the director.

303
00:12:01,560 --> 00:12:04,469
Basically, I'm her right-hand man.

304
00:12:04,470 --> 00:12:05,670
Are you the assistant director?

305
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:08,199
You can put it that way.

306
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:10,580
- Anyway, I'm in the program department.
- Dai Daji!

307
00:12:11,040 --> 00:12:13,100
You see? They need me all the time.

308
00:12:13,710 --> 00:12:14,469
Director Wen.

309
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:15,679
The rubbish bin is full.

310
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:17,630
Don't you know
how to dispose of the trash?

311
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:18,839
Are you too free?

312
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,509
Where's my coffee?

313
00:12:20,510 --> 00:12:21,960
But this is Long's job.

314
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:24,520
So, you intend to stay out of it
just because it isn't your job?

315
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:26,079
- I...
- You don't want to be an intern?

316
00:12:26,080 --> 00:12:27,040
That's not it. I want to.

317
00:12:27,040 --> 00:12:29,560
- I'll get you a cup of coffee.
- Hurry and clean the place up.

318
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:32,040
You don't have any drive and still
want to become a full-time employee?

319
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:41,960
- So, you're an intern.
- My internship will end soon.

320
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,560
I'll become an official employee after that.

321
00:12:43,560 --> 00:12:46,060
By then, my lowest position
will be an assistant director.

322
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,670
Yiming, it's fine.
You should sit down. I'll do it.

323
00:13:01,590 --> 00:13:02,349
I'm done.

324
00:13:02,350 --> 00:13:03,679
I'll place your equipment here.

325
00:13:03,680 --> 00:13:04,709
Don't call me again.

326
00:13:04,710 --> 00:13:05,980
Brat.

327
00:13:07,710 --> 00:13:09,039
This is your pay.

328
00:13:09,040 --> 00:13:10,060
2,000 yuan.

329
00:13:10,590 --> 00:13:13,220
I can't just let you work for nothing.

330
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:17,039
I guess you don't like money.

331
00:13:17,040 --> 00:13:19,150
You're a noble and high-minded artist.

332
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,190
Reverb.

333
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:23,220
What's wrong?

334
00:13:25,560 --> 00:13:27,190
I guess I can take the money.

335
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:28,820
What did you say?

336
00:13:30,320 --> 00:13:32,630
I already did the work.
Why should I refuse the money?

337
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,159
There's one more job in three days.

338
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,980
If you come, I'll pay you.

339
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,340
Thanks.

340
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:44,910
Hurry up.

341
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:46,580
Do you guys want to get off work or not?

342
00:13:48,790 --> 00:13:50,389
(Necklace)

343
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:52,150
My goodness.

344
00:14:17,280 --> 00:14:18,550
Daji!

345
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:20,439
I'm back.

346
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,700
You're back.

347
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:23,839
What a tiring day.

348
00:14:23,840 --> 00:14:25,390
You should take a break.

349
00:14:25,590 --> 00:14:26,790
What are you doing?

350
00:14:26,920 --> 00:14:29,340
I'm looking at things
that are related to work.

351
00:14:31,510 --> 00:14:32,550
Daji.

352
00:14:33,230 --> 00:14:35,190
Your birthday is in a few more days.

353
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,869
Tell me what you want.

354
00:14:36,870 --> 00:14:38,589
I don't want anything.

355
00:14:38,590 --> 00:14:39,279
You see,

356
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:41,629
we have to be frugal.

357
00:14:41,630 --> 00:14:43,589
Don't talk about the cost.

358
00:14:43,590 --> 00:14:44,919
Just tell me what you want.

359
00:14:44,920 --> 00:14:46,940
I don't want anything.

360
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:49,190
Let's drop the topic.

361
00:14:49,320 --> 00:14:50,869
You filmed a movie today, right?

362
00:14:50,870 --> 00:14:52,349
What did you film?

363
00:14:52,350 --> 00:14:53,159
Do you have

364
00:14:53,160 --> 00:14:54,580
any materials that I can see?

365
00:14:54,710 --> 00:14:55,940
Where's your DV?

366
00:14:56,230 --> 00:14:58,199
I did film a movie.

367
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:00,109
But I want to organize
the materials first.

368
00:15:00,110 --> 00:15:00,799
It's fine.

369
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:02,469
I just want to see
what you've done today.

370
00:15:02,470 --> 00:15:03,860
I'll just check out the footage.

371
00:15:04,110 --> 00:15:06,150
- My DV is out of battery.
- Really?

372
00:15:06,160 --> 00:15:07,150
It's...

373
00:15:07,470 --> 00:15:08,959
I'll show you
the finished product later.

374
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:10,310
Don't be so impatient.

375
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,079
Alright.

376
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:16,310
Director Zhou, you have to work hard.
I'm waiting for your movie.

377
00:15:17,880 --> 00:15:20,589
- Let's talk about your birthday.
- No. Let's talk about your movie.

378
00:15:20,590 --> 00:15:24,279
Daji, you see, this is the first birthday
we're celebrating together.

379
00:15:24,280 --> 00:15:26,109
I have to buy you a birthday present.

380
00:15:26,110 --> 00:15:27,559
It's fine. You don't need to.

381
00:15:27,560 --> 00:15:28,919
I don't need anything.

382
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:29,799
You need them, Daji.

383
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:30,589
I don't.

384
00:15:30,590 --> 00:15:31,589
You need them.

385
00:15:31,590 --> 00:15:33,030
I'll use the restroom.

386
00:15:34,160 --> 00:15:35,109
Hurry and wash up.

387
00:15:35,110 --> 00:15:36,109
Daji, think about it.

388
00:15:36,110 --> 00:15:37,799
I'm serious.
Tell me when you've decided.

389
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:39,740
Alright. I'll tell you
when I've decided.

390
00:16:29,990 --> 00:16:32,669
(The 2008 Beijing Olympics
officially ended.)

391
00:16:32,669 --> 00:16:35,199
(The Chinese delegation ranked first
in the gold medal standings)

392
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:38,039
(with a total of 48 gold medals,
22 silver medals,)

393
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:39,749
(and 30 bronze medals,)

394
00:16:39,750 --> 00:16:42,079
(achieving China's best performance)

395
00:16:42,080 --> 00:16:43,820
(in Olympic history.)

396
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:54,580
Hello? Who is this?

397
00:16:57,470 --> 00:16:58,980
My surname is Dai.

398
00:16:59,280 --> 00:17:01,039
I don't know anyone like that.

399
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:02,039
Mom, it's me.

400
00:17:02,040 --> 00:17:03,799
I'm your dear daughter.

401
00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:04,870
Mom.

402
00:17:05,110 --> 00:17:06,519
Oh, I have a daughter, huh?

403
00:17:06,520 --> 00:17:08,500
I almost forgot about it.

404
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:11,189
What? You're still alive, huh?

405
00:17:11,190 --> 00:17:12,190
Mom.

406
00:17:12,800 --> 00:17:14,070
Can you lend me

407
00:17:14,590 --> 00:17:16,390
10,000 yuan?

408
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:18,629
How is that enough?

409
00:17:18,630 --> 00:17:20,200
Why don't I transfer you
100 million yuan?

410
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:20,780
That's not it.

411
00:17:21,150 --> 00:17:21,759
I...

412
00:17:21,760 --> 00:17:22,999
You see, I...

413
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,589
I'm sorry, okay?

414
00:17:24,590 --> 00:17:25,389
I'm sorry.

415
00:17:25,390 --> 00:17:26,949
I know that I'm lending money from you,

416
00:17:26,950 --> 00:17:28,999
and that I'm a total embarrassment.

417
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:31,149
But I'm truly in trouble.

418
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:32,799
Dai Daji, be honest with me.

419
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:34,589
What were you doing in Beijing?

420
00:17:34,590 --> 00:17:35,629
I'm working there.

421
00:17:35,630 --> 00:17:38,070
I'm working for the show
called "Beautiful."

422
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:39,869
So, you're working.

423
00:17:39,870 --> 00:17:41,279
Even so, you're asking me for money?

424
00:17:41,280 --> 00:17:43,239
Where's your own money?
How did you spend them?

425
00:17:43,240 --> 00:17:45,949
I'm an intern, you know?

426
00:17:45,950 --> 00:17:46,949
I'm just an intern.

427
00:17:46,950 --> 00:17:49,719
My wage is very low.
I'm not even an official employee.

428
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,020
Have you got into a relationship?

429
00:17:51,150 --> 00:17:52,500
How did you know?

430
00:17:54,110 --> 00:17:56,839
You're asking me for money
when you're working.

431
00:17:56,840 --> 00:17:58,039
It's not like you have no wage.

432
00:17:58,040 --> 00:17:59,589
Your life is a total mess.

433
00:17:59,590 --> 00:18:01,189
Of course you're doing this

434
00:18:01,190 --> 00:18:02,590
for the sake of a stupid man.

435
00:18:02,760 --> 00:18:04,429
No.

436
00:18:04,430 --> 00:18:05,780
That's definitely not it.

437
00:18:06,110 --> 00:18:08,279
I'll explain it to you later.

438
00:18:08,280 --> 00:18:09,239
Anyway, right now,

439
00:18:09,240 --> 00:18:13,109
I'm truly in a lot of trouble
and at my wit's end. That's why I'm begging you.

440
00:18:13,110 --> 00:18:15,220
Would it kill you
to help me out just this time?

441
00:18:15,280 --> 00:18:17,039
If you're in trouble,

442
00:18:17,040 --> 00:18:18,560
why don't you find your boyfriend?

443
00:18:18,560 --> 00:18:20,120
Why are you trying
to borrow money from me?

444
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:21,820
I don't have any money.
I'm not lending you any.

445
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:22,940
Mom!

446
00:18:23,390 --> 00:18:24,350
Mom!

447
00:18:24,910 --> 00:18:26,260
Deng Xiaoya!

448
00:18:30,240 --> 00:18:31,980
I'll jump off the building!

449
00:18:49,910 --> 00:18:50,780
Miss.

450
00:18:52,000 --> 00:18:55,140
You see, I think you gave me less wage
than I was supposed to receive.

451
00:18:55,140 --> 00:18:57,629
I make 300 yuan for each episode we record.
We've done 8 episodes.

452
00:18:57,629 --> 00:18:58,839
You should pay me 2,400 yuan.

453
00:18:58,840 --> 00:19:00,630
Why did you only pay me 2,000 yuan?

454
00:19:00,840 --> 00:19:03,039
I got it. I'll have my lunch first.
We can talk about it later.

455
00:19:03,040 --> 00:19:04,719
Hey, you... You're having lunch first?

456
00:19:04,720 --> 00:19:06,540
What's wrong with you?

457
00:19:09,430 --> 00:19:10,940
Why are you standing there?

458
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:13,189
Yiming? What are you doing here?

459
00:19:13,190 --> 00:19:15,150
I'm here to attend a meeting
with your HOD.

460
00:19:15,480 --> 00:19:16,740
You haven't eaten yet, right?

461
00:19:17,040 --> 00:19:18,630
I have.

462
00:19:19,240 --> 00:19:20,279
I'm sure you haven't.

463
00:19:20,280 --> 00:19:21,589
Don't be so courteous with me.

464
00:19:21,590 --> 00:19:22,999
Come on. Let's go.

465
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:24,239
- I...
- It's my treat.

466
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:24,839
Let's go.

467
00:19:24,840 --> 00:19:27,079
It doesn't change the fact
that I've eaten.

468
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:29,460
It's my first time
coming to Blue Harbor.

469
00:19:29,590 --> 00:19:30,999
You're so courteous.

470
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:33,740
You're even buying me desserts.

471
00:19:34,040 --> 00:19:35,109
Don't stand on ceremony.

472
00:19:35,110 --> 00:19:35,999
Eat up.

473
00:19:36,000 --> 00:19:37,869
Aren't desserts the craze nowadays?

474
00:19:37,870 --> 00:19:38,870
Yeah.

475
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:40,540
Thank you, Yiming.

476
00:19:42,430 --> 00:19:43,479
Look at you.

477
00:19:43,480 --> 00:19:45,589
You devote yourself to work
the entire day.

478
00:19:45,590 --> 00:19:46,909
You didn't eat well.

479
00:19:46,910 --> 00:19:49,189
Why are you trying to tire yourself out?

480
00:19:49,190 --> 00:19:51,589
I can't remain in Beijing
unless I strive hard.

481
00:19:51,590 --> 00:19:54,300
There are plenty of ways
for you to remain in Beijing.

482
00:19:54,590 --> 00:19:55,389
For example,

483
00:19:55,390 --> 00:19:57,560
you can get married to a man
with a Beijing hukou.

484
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:59,149
After that, you can raise his children.

485
00:19:59,150 --> 00:20:01,079
You can remain in Beijing
using that method as well.

486
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:04,110
No way. My boyfriend is from Sichuan.

487
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:05,540
So, you have a boyfriend, huh?

488
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:07,349
He's my university coursemate.

489
00:20:07,350 --> 00:20:08,559
We came to Beijing together.

490
00:20:08,560 --> 00:20:10,500
Is he working on the show
together with you?

491
00:20:10,950 --> 00:20:12,110
No.

492
00:20:12,350 --> 00:20:13,940
He has a different job.

493
00:20:14,110 --> 00:20:16,070
He's a movie director.

494
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:17,740
A movie director?

495
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:19,780
That's pretty outstanding.

496
00:20:20,000 --> 00:20:21,519
Has he directed any famous movies?

497
00:20:21,520 --> 00:20:22,910
Any movies that I've seen before?

498
00:20:24,280 --> 00:20:26,390
He's directing a movie now.

499
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:27,839
I'll invite you to its premiere

500
00:20:27,840 --> 00:20:28,799
once it's ready.

501
00:20:28,800 --> 00:20:29,870
Okay.

502
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:31,669
You're pretty confident in him, huh?

503
00:20:31,670 --> 00:20:32,589
That's not it.

504
00:20:32,590 --> 00:20:34,519
You see, you just haven't met him before.

505
00:20:34,520 --> 00:20:35,869
If you do see him,

506
00:20:35,870 --> 00:20:38,279
you can tell that he's talented
at first glance.

507
00:20:38,280 --> 00:20:39,319
Look at you.

508
00:20:39,320 --> 00:20:41,940
Your eyes are glowing
when you talk about him.

509
00:20:42,000 --> 00:20:43,870
Do you idolize him?

510
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:47,390
It's not that serious.
I don't think I idolize him.

511
00:20:47,840 --> 00:20:49,039
But,

512
00:20:49,040 --> 00:20:51,390
he's quite different from us.

513
00:20:52,590 --> 00:20:54,070
In what way?

514
00:20:54,390 --> 00:20:55,669
Usually,

515
00:20:55,670 --> 00:20:57,799
we only mind our own businesses.

516
00:20:57,800 --> 00:20:59,910
We lead realistic lives.

517
00:21:00,150 --> 00:21:02,350
We don't have any lofty aspirations.

518
00:21:02,430 --> 00:21:04,020
But he's different.

519
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:06,390
His eyes radiate brilliance.

520
00:21:06,720 --> 00:21:08,540
He has a story to tell.

521
00:21:08,670 --> 00:21:10,719
He's a true idealist.

522
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:12,260
He's very charming.

523
00:21:12,390 --> 00:21:13,839
I think he'll definitely be

524
00:21:13,840 --> 00:21:15,670
an amazing movie director in the future.

525
00:21:18,080 --> 00:21:19,319
- Mr. Zhou, come here.
- Coming.

526
00:21:19,319 --> 00:21:20,669
Take photos of the couple
seeing their guests off.

527
00:21:20,670 --> 00:21:23,300
- Alright. Give me a moment.
- That's right. That's the scene. Quickly.

528
00:21:23,520 --> 00:21:24,519
Make it look nicer.

529
00:21:24,520 --> 00:21:26,780
There are plenty of directors now, huh?

530
00:21:26,840 --> 00:21:28,740
They even have a director
for a wedding ceremony.

531
00:21:30,520 --> 00:21:31,780
Zhou Shui.

532
00:21:32,840 --> 00:21:33,909
The wedding is over.

533
00:21:33,910 --> 00:21:36,589
But you need to shoot
some footage of the guests eating.

534
00:21:36,590 --> 00:21:37,630
Okay.

535
00:21:40,560 --> 00:21:43,429
Come, Zhou Shui. Shoot some footage
of them clinking their glass. Come.

536
00:21:43,430 --> 00:21:45,389
- Zhou Shui, over here.
- Alright. Don't worry.

537
00:21:45,390 --> 00:21:46,909
- Shoot from this angle.
- Alright.

538
00:21:46,910 --> 00:21:48,999
Give this dish a special feature.

539
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:49,910
Here.

540
00:21:53,910 --> 00:21:55,070
Daji?

541
00:21:55,190 --> 00:21:56,300
What are you doing here?

542
00:21:56,670 --> 00:21:58,150
What are you doing here?

543
00:21:58,520 --> 00:21:59,149
Mr. Zhou.

544
00:21:59,150 --> 00:22:01,239
Are you filming a wedding?

545
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:03,189
Have you been filming weddings
for the past few days?

546
00:22:03,190 --> 00:22:04,460
- That's not it.
- Zhou Shui.

547
00:22:04,480 --> 00:22:06,589
- Sorry about this. I know.
- I won't let you do it!

548
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:07,630
Come here for a second.

549
00:22:08,240 --> 00:22:09,559
Can you stop messing around?

550
00:22:09,560 --> 00:22:11,830
- I'm still working.
- I'm not.

551
00:22:11,870 --> 00:22:13,109
Why did you lie to me?

552
00:22:13,110 --> 00:22:15,139
If I don't work now,
both of us won't make any money.

553
00:22:15,139 --> 00:22:17,239
We're barely surviving, you know?
What choice do I have?

554
00:22:17,240 --> 00:22:18,960
I don't know
the kind of life you desire.

555
00:22:18,960 --> 00:22:21,560
I want to be rich enough
to sleep in a room with air-conditioner,

556
00:22:21,560 --> 00:22:25,020
to provide you with a good life,
and to buy you presents during your birthday.

557
00:22:25,560 --> 00:22:28,190
I never wanted you
to buy any gifts for me.

558
00:22:28,950 --> 00:22:31,000
What about the platinum necklace
on your laptop screen?

559
00:22:31,000 --> 00:22:32,220
Isn't that what you desire?

560
00:22:32,560 --> 00:22:33,620
I was checking that website

561
00:22:33,620 --> 00:22:36,319
because our client's necklace
used as a product placement went missing.

562
00:22:36,320 --> 00:22:38,220
They insisted on making me
compensate them for it.

563
00:22:38,220 --> 00:22:39,980
If not, I'll lose my job.

564
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:42,540
That's a huge deal.
Why didn't you tell me about it?

565
00:22:43,590 --> 00:22:44,519
Why should I tell you?

566
00:22:44,520 --> 00:22:46,220
You have a movie to film.

567
00:22:46,840 --> 00:22:48,109
I can't film movies now.

568
00:22:48,110 --> 00:22:50,680
My DV is broken. I don't even
have enough money to repair it, Daji.

569
00:22:50,680 --> 00:22:51,999
- Hurry up.
- When did that happen?

570
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,319
You didn't tell me about it either.

571
00:22:53,320 --> 00:22:55,300
- That day, I...
- Brat, what are you doing?

572
00:22:56,190 --> 00:22:56,999
Reverb.

573
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,189
I'll handle this, okay?

574
00:22:58,190 --> 00:23:00,869
Girl, don't bother him.

575
00:23:00,870 --> 00:23:03,110
- Your man is trying to make money now.
- What's going on?

576
00:23:03,390 --> 00:23:04,419
Who are you?

577
00:23:04,419 --> 00:23:05,799
- Who are you? Don't touch me.
- Wait!

578
00:23:05,800 --> 00:23:06,839
Who are you? Don't touch me.

579
00:23:06,840 --> 00:23:08,189
I know both of you.

580
00:23:08,190 --> 00:23:09,719
This is my senior, Yang Yiming.

581
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:11,260
This is my boyfriend, Zhou Shui.

582
00:23:12,560 --> 00:23:15,149
I've long heard of your name.
She mentioned you just now.

583
00:23:15,150 --> 00:23:16,669
She said you were a movie director.

584
00:23:16,670 --> 00:23:19,319
Why are you
a wedding video director now?

585
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:20,590
What are you doing?

586
00:23:21,240 --> 00:23:22,500
Are you still doing it or not?

587
00:23:22,800 --> 00:23:24,700
Can you be professional for once?

588
00:23:26,350 --> 00:23:27,670
Where's the photographer?

589
00:23:27,760 --> 00:23:29,589
Hurry up.
We have another job after this.

590
00:23:29,590 --> 00:23:30,279
Hey, Mr. Zhou.

591
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:32,670
That's right! So what if
I'm a wedding video director?

592
00:23:34,760 --> 00:23:35,869
Zhou Shui, what's wrong of you?

593
00:23:35,870 --> 00:23:37,300
You were too mean.

594
00:23:37,550 --> 00:23:39,900
(We got married)

595
00:23:41,840 --> 00:23:43,500
Enough. Don't be angry.

596
00:23:43,560 --> 00:23:45,500
Why don't we head back
and continue our meal?

597
00:24:10,320 --> 00:24:12,190
She asked me why I didn't film movies.

598
00:24:12,760 --> 00:24:14,350
She asked me why I went to make money.

599
00:24:16,520 --> 00:24:18,500
Why can't she understand?

600
00:24:21,040 --> 00:24:22,460
I understand

601
00:24:23,080 --> 00:24:25,300
why he took on other jobs.

602
00:24:27,390 --> 00:24:29,870
Actually, I wasn't angry at him.

603
00:24:31,590 --> 00:24:34,020
I was angry at myself.

604
00:24:36,000 --> 00:24:38,590
I said I would make money to support him

605
00:24:38,670 --> 00:24:40,500
so that he could film movies.

606
00:24:41,910 --> 00:24:44,190
But I'm not capable enough to do so.

607
00:24:45,430 --> 00:24:47,460
I know she's under huge pressure.

608
00:24:48,670 --> 00:24:50,390
She has to pay our rent,

609
00:24:50,630 --> 00:24:52,190
provide for both of us,

610
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:55,390
and compensate her client
with an expensive necklace.

611
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:59,830
This should be
my responsibility as a man.

612
00:25:03,720 --> 00:25:06,500
I just can't get used to the fact
that he's taking jobs.

613
00:25:08,150 --> 00:25:10,630
He's a proud artist.

614
00:25:11,320 --> 00:25:13,020
But in order to make money,

615
00:25:14,430 --> 00:25:15,870
he has to bow down.

616
00:25:16,080 --> 00:25:18,220
He's letting people ordering him around.

617
00:25:19,320 --> 00:25:21,260
I don't want him
to become someone like that.

618
00:25:43,950 --> 00:25:45,830
Happy birthday, Daji.

619
00:25:52,520 --> 00:25:53,700
Thank you.

620
00:25:55,280 --> 00:25:57,980
Today's your birthday.
Can you get off work early?

621
00:25:59,590 --> 00:26:01,150
I don't know.

622
00:26:03,040 --> 00:26:04,190
What about you?

623
00:26:04,870 --> 00:26:06,540
Do you have wedding jobs today?

624
00:26:09,350 --> 00:26:12,020
I'll try my best
to end it as soon as possible.

625
00:26:14,320 --> 00:26:15,460
Alright, then.

626
00:26:24,910 --> 00:26:30,580
(Spring 2024, Beijing)

627
00:26:30,840 --> 00:26:31,909
The client is rushing us.

628
00:26:31,910 --> 00:26:33,870
Therefore, we must be quick today.

629
00:26:34,110 --> 00:26:35,279
Hello.

630
00:26:35,280 --> 00:26:37,319
Tong Leyi asked me to come here.

631
00:26:37,320 --> 00:26:38,239
Over here.

632
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:39,980
- Come here.
- Thank you.

633
00:26:46,870 --> 00:26:48,590
You're actually having
a flash marriage, huh?

634
00:26:48,760 --> 00:26:51,279
It's all because you didn't stop me
from praying to Yue Lao.

635
00:26:51,280 --> 00:26:53,780
I had no choice but to take on
this wedding promotion.

636
00:26:53,840 --> 00:26:55,260
Is it that effective?

637
00:26:55,910 --> 00:26:57,350
Go inside and get changed.

638
00:26:58,080 --> 00:26:59,479
What outfit am I changing into?

639
00:26:59,480 --> 00:27:00,589
The groom's suit.

640
00:27:00,590 --> 00:27:02,999
My male partner stood me up suddenly.

641
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:04,389
I couldn't find anyone else.

642
00:27:04,390 --> 00:27:05,839
You have to be the one.

643
00:27:05,840 --> 00:27:06,940
Go inside.

644
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:11,079
You must be kidding me.

645
00:27:11,080 --> 00:27:12,460
I'm not.

646
00:27:13,480 --> 00:27:14,830
Your hands should be closer.

647
00:27:14,910 --> 00:27:16,559
I don't understand.

648
00:27:16,560 --> 00:27:18,799
Being a wedding video director
is pretty lucrative.

649
00:27:18,800 --> 00:27:21,350
Why did Zhou Shui and Daji argue, then?

650
00:27:22,390 --> 00:27:23,870
Change your pose.

651
00:27:24,040 --> 00:27:25,980
To Daji,

652
00:27:26,760 --> 00:27:28,910
Zhou Shui is an artist.

653
00:27:29,040 --> 00:27:31,540
His only job is to make movies.

654
00:27:32,150 --> 00:27:34,430
She's just like my mother.

655
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:36,540
When I was young,
I wanted to learn skateboard.

656
00:27:36,870 --> 00:27:38,759
She insisted on making me learn piano.

657
00:27:38,760 --> 00:27:39,830
Closer.

658
00:27:40,840 --> 00:27:44,629
Is Zhou Shui her son or her boyfriend?

659
00:27:44,630 --> 00:27:47,319
Isn't this just like the lyrics
in "Mother Is The Best?"

660
00:27:47,320 --> 00:27:49,430
Be serious. We're working.

661
00:27:53,320 --> 00:27:54,460
Stand closer to me.

662
00:27:57,280 --> 00:27:58,110
Okay.

663
00:27:58,280 --> 00:27:59,239
Sorry about that.

664
00:27:59,240 --> 00:28:01,190
I forgot that your mother
isn't around anymore.

665
00:28:01,520 --> 00:28:02,700
It's fine.

666
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:04,719
Change your pose.

667
00:28:04,720 --> 00:28:05,559
Face each other.

668
00:28:05,560 --> 00:28:06,519
Okay.

669
00:28:06,520 --> 00:28:08,150
Hold his hands.

670
00:28:08,430 --> 00:28:10,940
Make it like a wedding. Say "Yes, I do."

671
00:28:14,910 --> 00:28:15,870
I...

672
00:28:16,110 --> 00:28:17,070
I...

673
00:28:17,350 --> 00:28:18,460
Yes, I do.

674
00:28:21,840 --> 00:28:22,479
What's wrong?

675
00:28:22,480 --> 00:28:23,740
Zhang Shiyu!

676
00:28:24,950 --> 00:28:26,109
What are you doing here?

677
00:28:26,110 --> 00:28:27,719
Didn't you say you were
on a business trip?

678
00:28:27,720 --> 00:28:28,759
Who's that?

679
00:28:28,760 --> 00:28:29,629
So,

680
00:28:29,630 --> 00:28:30,630
she's my daughter.

681
00:28:30,800 --> 00:28:31,980
Who is he?

682
00:28:34,240 --> 00:28:35,079
He's my colleague.

683
00:28:35,080 --> 00:28:36,430
Hurry and greet Mr. Wang.

684
00:28:37,110 --> 00:28:38,780
You two disgust me.

685
00:28:40,320 --> 00:28:41,980
Let's go out another day.

686
00:28:42,190 --> 00:28:43,279
Who's that?

687
00:28:43,280 --> 00:28:44,239
My mother.

688
00:28:44,240 --> 00:28:45,559
Wasn't she dead?

689
00:28:45,560 --> 00:28:47,500
Where were we? Let's continue.

690
00:28:49,150 --> 00:28:51,079
Do it. Say "Yes, I do."

691
00:28:51,080 --> 00:28:51,980
I...

692
00:28:52,560 --> 00:28:54,260
Out with it.

693
00:28:55,080 --> 00:28:56,039
Yes, I do.

694
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:57,109
That's so fake.

695
00:28:57,110 --> 00:28:59,740
"Yes, I do" is the fakest term
in the world.

696
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:05,910
Brat.

697
00:29:07,150 --> 00:29:08,239
You did a good job today.

698
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:10,500
The client gave you
an extra 1,000 yuan bonus.

699
00:29:10,670 --> 00:29:12,780
I knew you were talented.

700
00:29:13,590 --> 00:29:14,830
Keep it up.

701
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:17,150
I can't do this job forever.

702
00:29:17,190 --> 00:29:18,350
I'll say this first.

703
00:29:18,430 --> 00:29:20,540
I'll quit after making enough

704
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:22,110
to buy Daji's necklace.

705
00:29:22,800 --> 00:29:24,500
It's easy for you to say.

706
00:29:24,670 --> 00:29:27,500
Why would you want to quit
when you're making money here?

707
00:29:28,590 --> 00:29:30,980
There's another job tonight.
Remember to come.

708
00:29:32,670 --> 00:29:33,980
Did you hear me?

709
00:29:35,910 --> 00:29:37,540
What a stubborn boy.

710
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:48,020
So,

711
00:29:48,430 --> 00:29:50,150
the brand dealer called us.

712
00:29:50,320 --> 00:29:51,460
What did they say?

713
00:29:51,670 --> 00:29:53,870
They said they would retrieve
the necklace this afternoon.

714
00:29:54,430 --> 00:29:55,740
I'm done for.

715
00:29:55,760 --> 00:29:57,350
I haven't saved up enough money yet.

716
00:30:02,040 --> 00:30:02,949
I have an idea.

717
00:30:02,950 --> 00:30:04,220
What is it?

718
00:30:08,280 --> 00:30:10,589
They signed a contract
with our company, not us.

719
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:11,669
We're just interns.

720
00:30:11,670 --> 00:30:13,079
We didn't sign
any labor contracts either.

721
00:30:13,080 --> 00:30:14,910
They won't be able
to press charges against us.

722
00:30:15,110 --> 00:30:17,020
I suggest you resign immediately.

723
00:30:18,590 --> 00:30:19,830
You want me to leave?

724
00:30:20,320 --> 00:30:21,460
Yeah.

725
00:30:23,150 --> 00:30:25,070
But today's my birthday.

726
00:30:25,630 --> 00:30:28,430
I don't want to lose
my job on my birthday.

727
00:30:30,080 --> 00:30:32,780
Why must it be today?

728
00:30:38,070 --> 00:30:41,860
(Transaction Notice:
You have received 10,000 yuan.)

729
00:30:46,430 --> 00:30:48,452
(Mom: I'm doing this
for the sake of Beautiful.)

730
00:30:48,453 --> 00:30:51,620
(I'm donating the money to you as a fan
of the show. Do your best on the show.)

731
00:31:02,240 --> 00:31:03,999
I'll buy you a meal next time.

732
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:04,949
Good job, Wen.

733
00:31:04,950 --> 00:31:06,880
Look after your father.
He's a little drunk.

734
00:31:07,239 --> 00:31:09,039
Take note of this
when you clean up the venue.

735
00:31:09,040 --> 00:31:09,519
Take care.

736
00:31:09,520 --> 00:31:10,799
Put these wine bottles together.

737
00:31:10,800 --> 00:31:13,190
- The groom wants to take them back.
- Okay.

738
00:31:15,560 --> 00:31:16,589
Young man.

739
00:31:16,590 --> 00:31:18,949
You're the best photographer here.

740
00:31:18,950 --> 00:31:20,479
Can you help us
take another group photo?

741
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:21,349
- No problem.
- Okay.

742
00:31:21,350 --> 00:31:22,109
Thank you so much.

743
00:31:22,110 --> 00:31:23,319
Don't mention it.

744
00:31:23,320 --> 00:31:26,239
In-law, come. We didn't take
any nice photos or eat well just now.

745
00:31:26,240 --> 00:31:27,189
Come. Hurry.

746
00:31:27,190 --> 00:31:28,319
Hurry. Come here.

747
00:31:28,320 --> 00:31:28,759
Here.

748
00:31:28,760 --> 00:31:29,940
Over here.

749
00:31:30,480 --> 00:31:32,540
Okay.

750
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:34,949
Three, two, one.

751
00:31:34,950 --> 00:31:35,559
Alright.

752
00:31:35,560 --> 00:31:37,429
- Thank you, hunk.
- Good job. See if it's okay.

753
00:31:37,430 --> 00:31:39,429
Yeah. This looks great. Thank you.

754
00:31:39,430 --> 00:31:42,039
- I'll send it to you later. Congratulations.
- Thank you, young man.

755
00:31:42,040 --> 00:31:42,949
Thank you.

756
00:31:42,950 --> 00:31:43,629
Good job.

757
00:31:43,630 --> 00:31:45,400
The next group
will enter the venue soon.

758
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:46,940
Everyone should hurry up.

759
00:31:47,150 --> 00:31:47,940
I...

760
00:31:48,240 --> 00:31:49,239
Where's my food?

761
00:31:49,240 --> 00:31:51,110
Sorry. I've disposed of it.

762
00:31:53,190 --> 00:31:54,239
It's fine.

763
00:31:54,240 --> 00:31:55,390
Alright.

764
00:32:02,350 --> 00:32:04,559
Can you clean up that table later?

765
00:32:04,560 --> 00:32:05,429
Sure.

766
00:32:05,430 --> 00:32:06,630
Thank you.

767
00:32:11,830 --> 00:32:38,820
(Dramatic Effect, Please Do Not Imitate)

768
00:32:45,520 --> 00:32:46,559
- What?
- Why are you here?

769
00:32:46,560 --> 00:32:47,589
What are you doing here?

770
00:32:47,590 --> 00:32:49,350
Aren't you going
to wish me Happy Birthday?

771
00:32:49,910 --> 00:32:51,540
Happy birthday, Daji.

772
00:32:53,840 --> 00:32:56,070
Let's go. I'll treat you to a feast.

773
00:32:56,670 --> 00:32:57,559
Give me a second.

774
00:32:57,560 --> 00:32:58,830
Let me keep my things.

775
00:32:59,760 --> 00:33:00,670
Let's go.

776
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:03,430
What do you want to eat today?

777
00:33:04,670 --> 00:33:05,719
What are you eating?

778
00:33:05,720 --> 00:33:06,870
Mango.

779
00:33:07,430 --> 00:33:08,949
Don't eat people's leftovers.

780
00:33:08,950 --> 00:33:10,319
Come. Let's go and eat.

781
00:33:10,320 --> 00:33:12,279
It's fine. There are plenty of food left.

782
00:33:12,280 --> 00:33:14,429
We have a free feast here.
Why are we eating outside?

783
00:33:14,430 --> 00:33:16,239
Stop eating them. They're cold.

784
00:33:16,240 --> 00:33:18,559
It's free. I don't care if it's cold.

785
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:19,479
My goodness.

786
00:33:19,480 --> 00:33:20,910
Hurry and sit down.

787
00:33:25,520 --> 00:33:26,830
It's delicious.

788
00:33:28,800 --> 00:33:30,110
There's chicken as well.

789
00:33:32,240 --> 00:33:33,279
Eat up.

790
00:33:33,280 --> 00:33:35,350
Why don't you dare
to go crazy with me anymore?

791
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:37,260
There's lobster as well.

792
00:33:38,840 --> 00:33:40,079
Who said there's nothing left?

793
00:33:40,080 --> 00:33:41,150
Fine.

794
00:33:43,110 --> 00:33:43,980
I'll join you.

795
00:33:44,950 --> 00:33:47,150
Let's drink, then.

796
00:33:47,320 --> 00:33:48,350
Alright.

797
00:33:52,040 --> 00:33:52,980
Cheers.

798
00:33:53,760 --> 00:33:54,980
Happy birthday.

799
00:33:59,080 --> 00:34:00,220
Let's do this.

800
00:34:26,280 --> 00:34:27,420
I'm sorry.

801
00:34:27,470 --> 00:34:28,590
For what?

802
00:34:28,720 --> 00:34:30,469
You have to eat leftovers
on your birthday.

803
00:34:30,470 --> 00:34:31,599
How are these leftovers?

804
00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:33,070
We were just late.

805
00:34:33,160 --> 00:34:34,639
I have to apologize to you instead.

